com.vub.model

Class Program

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vub.model.Program

  • @Entity
public class Program
extends java.lang.Object
    This class models programs. A program is the entire bachelors degree, or the entire masters degree. In this program, trajects are stored - a traject is one specific year in the program.
